Become a Member of Legends Golf & Country Club
Membership is an important part of our business, and we acknowledge that by providing our members with an exclusive golfing experience. Make new connections or catch up with old friends. Play when you want to play without worrying about the budget.
We are currently accepting new members. Please use the contact below to discuss Membership options
.
We have a limited number of Annual Range Memberships available for purchase. Single Annual Range Membership is only $500.00 or Family Annual Range Membership is only $700.00. Filling up fast, ACT NOW!
